<template lang="pug">
    .container
        md-card
            md-card-header
                md-card-header-text Select Filters:
            md-card-content
                FilterCard(v-for="filter in filters")
            md-card-actions
                md-button.md-primary.md-raised Add Filter
                md-button.md-accent.md-raised Submit


</template>



<script>

    import FilterCard from './FilterCard.vue'
    export default {
        name: "FilterView",
        data () {
            return {
                filters: ["filter1"]
            }
        },
        components: {
            FilterCard
        }
    }
</script>

<style scoped lang="stylus">


</style>
